I. Definitions
"The Software" refers to the Curio Trinkets Bridge mod and all of its source code,
resource files, and build artifacts.
"The Author" refers to the copyright holder,Song Mingyu (宋明禹).
"Derivative Works" refers to any software created, modified, or extended based on
all or part of the code of The Software.

II. Grant of Rights
Subject to full compliance with all terms of this License, The Author grants you
the following limited rights:
1. To use The Software for personal, non-commercial purposes.
2. To read and study the source code of The Software.
3. To create Derivative Works based on The Software's code, provided that such
   Derivative Works comply with all terms of this License.

III. Restrictions
1. [No Unauthorized Commercial Use] Without prior written authorization from
   The Author, no individual, company, or organization may use The Software or
   its Derivative Works for any commercial purpose, including but not limited to
   selling, paid downloads, embedding advertisements for profit, or providing
   as part of a commercial service.
2. [No Unauthorized Distribution] Without prior written authorization from
   The Author, no third-party company, platform, or individual may publish,
   distribute, or redistribute The Software in any form (including compiled
   binaries and source code). The Software may only be obtained through
   official channels designated by The Author.
3. [Source Attribution] Any mod or software that uses all or part of
   The Software's code must clearly attribute the source in a prominent location
   (including but not limited to README, license files, and mod description pages),
